						               													<description>Lucky Flip is the fun-for-all roulette style party game that pits family and friends against each other in a lively challenge of strategy, memory, &amp;amp; luck. There are 53 total cards in the deck- forty cards numbered 1-40, 10 Lucky Pot Cards, and 3 Lucky Flip cards. The objective of this game is to win more points than your opponents by correctly guessing what each card will reveal once flipped over. To increase the chances of winning even more points, players must rely on their memory to avoid guessing cards that were already flipped and removed from the deck. Playing Lucky Flip is as easy as 1, 2, 3!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;~Each player receives 7 tokens to start the game and attempts to guess what the top card will reveal once flipped over by placing all their tokens on the game board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;~Top Card is flipped over to see who won points:&amp;#10;1 point- Guess the correct color&amp;#10;2 points- Guess the correct group of numbers&amp;#10;3 points- For every token on a winning number&amp;#10;10 or 30 points- Guess the Lucky Pot card&amp;#10;100 points- Guess the Lucky Flip card&amp;#10;~Players on winning number roll the dice to double their total points won for that round&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This fast-paced party game is easy to learn and play, making it perfect for players at all skill levels and those ages 12 and up. The rules are short and simple; making it easy to convince friends and family to gather around. With 2 &amp;ndash; 6 players, Lucky Flip promise to be an exciting game where everyone leaves as happy as the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective of the game is to earn points by correctly guessing what the top card on the deck will reveal by placing your tokens on the Lucky Flip game board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
